<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa a bochan mi cu, Zion tlang bantuk an si
 Thihnak um lo, thir le phang um lo,
 Tlang hna nih Jeruslam, khua thiang, an kulh bang in
 Bawipa nih, a mi hna, a kan kulh cang.

[C1]
   Jesuh cu ka himnak, Jesuh cu ka dornak
   Jesuh cu ka caa nunnak a si
   Ka nunnak cu Bawipa Jesuh, amah lawng a si
   Ka lawm khun, Halleluijah a men.

[V2]
 Bawipa a bochan mi cu, Tiva pawng thingkung bangin
 Amah caan ah, thei a tlai zungzal,
 A hnah zong a uai bal lo, a thei zong ttil bal lo
 A tuahnak, kip ah mi thlachuak a si.

[V3]
 Kei ka lunglawmhnak bik cu, Bawipa Jesuh lawng asi
 Amah lo cun, lawmh a tling kho lo,
 Jesuh khrih ka ngeih cang ca'h, Vawlei ro ka tum lo
 Mi lunglawm, mi thluachuak, Jesuh ka ngei.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA A BOCHAN MI HNA</title>
</song>